@host = http://localhost:5001

### Health check  -> 200 "Healthy"
GET {{host}}/health

### Register a new account  -> 201 Created
POST {{host}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "hunter2pw"
}

### Login with the correct password  -> 200 OK (user info)
POST {{host}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "hunter2pw"
}

### Login with a wrong password  -> 401 Unauthorized
POST {{host}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "wrong-password"
}

### Register the same email again  -> 400 Bad Request (already exists)
POST {{host}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "another"
}
